title: Double Trouble 2022: Browns & Ravens
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp tackle a Double Trouble on the Browns and Ravens, including if Kareem Hunt is a weekly starter and when is too early to draft Mark Andrews. Then, the guys talk their biggest draft day concerns.
